I"¥<h2 id="learning-goals">Learning Goals</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Understand how cookies are a part of the request/response cycle</li>
  <li>Explain different use cases for sessions, cookies, and flashes</li>
  <li>Understand how to store state in both cookies and sessions</li>
  <li>Practice the syntax for setting and fetching session data</li>
  <li>Practice setting flash messages based on conditionals</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="structure">Structure</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Whiteboard discussion: Request/Response Cycle</li>
  <li>Video, Reading, &amp; Code Along</li>
  <li>Q&amp;A + Begin Homework</li>
</ul>

